OL,6,FLabour's Jo Stevens admitted that
OL,7,Fthere needs to be improvement to the
OL,8,Fhealth service in Wales.JShe said:
OL,9,F"We're training a record number of
OL,10,Fdoctors and nurses in Wales... and we
OL,11,Fstill have free prescriptions plus the
OL,12,FNHS bursary which the Tories cancelled
OL,13,Fin England."
OL,15,FPlaid Cymru's Liz Saville Roberts said
OL,16,Fcarers need to be paid more than #12
OL,17,Fan hour. "We have to pay people more
OL,18,Fthan that so it actually shows greater
OL,19,Fvalue to people who look after people,
OL,20,Fthan people who stack supermarket
OL,21,Fshelves."
