OL,6,FImmigration
OL,8,FDavid TC Davies, who has served as
OL,9,FSecretary of State for Wales, was
OL,10,Fquizzed on the Conservatives record on
OL,11,Fimmigration, which has risen over the
OL,12,Fpast 14 years.
OL,14,F"We haven't succeeded in stopping
OL,15,Fpeople completely," he said. "Millions
OL,16,Fof people are waiting in Africa to
OL,17,Fcome over."
