OL,6,FLiz Saville Roberts criticised the way
OL,7,Fpoliticians talking about immigration,
OL,8,Fsaying the debate has become
OL,9,F"poisoned".JShe added: "There is
OL,10,Fsomething about our politics which has
OL,11,Fchosen to pick on some of the weakest
OL,12,Fpeople and to turn them into demons."
OL,14,FFormer First Minister Mark Drakeford
OL,15,Fpreviously said that Wales needs more
OL,16,Fimmigration - and Jo Stevens was asked
OL,17,Fif she agrees.J"I come from Cardiff,
OL,18,Four city is built from immigration,"
OL,19,Fshe replied. "We wouldn't be where we
OL,20,Fare without immigration."
